==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untangle
<hw>Un*tan"gle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>tangle</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from tangles or
intricacy; to disentangle; to resolve; <as>as, to <ex>untangle</ex>
thread</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Untangle</qex> but this cruel chain.</q>
<rj><qau>Prior.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untappice</ent>⟦br⟧
